data.description: Welcome to your new home in the Grand Blanc School District! This 4-bedroom, 2-bathroom gem is perfect for families. Enjoy a bright, open layout with a modern kitchen and a cozy master suite. The backyard is great for barbecues and relaxing. Conveniently located near expressways and amenities, it's a welcoming space to call your own. Don't miss out—schedule a showing today!
